                            <comment id="17709113" author="brandon.williams" created="Wed, 5 Apr 2023 21:11:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I noticed this test only started to appear (and fail) after &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-18262&quot; title=&quot;Switch checkstyle running only with JDK8 to be run with JDK11&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-18262&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-18262&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, perhaps due to running checkstyle for both j8 and j11?  I reverted it and ran a build &lt;a href=&quot;https://ci-cassandra.apache.org/job/Cassandra-devbranch/2410/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; where the test did not fail.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
